readable.content: A casual family stroll by the water . A man , woman , and little girl walk along a boardwalk beside a calm sea . Child , man , and woman walking near the water . The little girl in the pink shirt is walking ahead of a man and woman on the side of the body of water Two adults and a small girl walk along an ocean boardwalk .
